rComments: I never had a problem understanding Nancy. I feel that I really learnt a lot about the Alexander Technique through her and it has helped my performance and even my mental state. Suffering an injury during the semester also showed me her expertise. Change is not fast, but don't expect it to be. Keep an open mind! This class gives easy good grades.
teacherRatingTags: ['Gives good feedback', "Skip class? You won't pass."]
